leaving_soon.title: Leaving Soon!
leaving_soon.description: Catch 'em while you can — these great titles won't be around for long!

284014.title: Virgin Territory
284014.description: A rakish Florentine beds any virgin he gets his hands on until he falls for a lovely heiress in this Renaissance-age rom-com.

300448.title: Death At A Funeral
300448.description: After the unexpected death of a British patriarch, the dead man’s secrets leave the rest of his family with comical complications.

300462.title: Rain Man
300462.description: A pompous man learns that he has an autistic brother when his father dies and leaves his million-dollar estate to his sibling’s mental institution.

300511.title: Some Like It Hot
300511.description: After witnessing a shooting, two Chicago musicians head south disguised as female jazz artists. Their cover seems perfect...until love comes along.

301153.title: Leviathan
301153.description: An underwater exploration team is trapped five miles beneath the ocean's surface with a creature that cannot die and exists only to kill.

302793.title: Caught In The Crossfire
302793.description: Two detectives investigating a gang-related crime find themselves targeted by both gang members and crooked cops.

305015.title: Gorky Park
305015.description: In the Soviet Union, a Russian police officer is caught up in a twisted murder mystery when three bodies are discovered in Moscow’s Gorky Park.

305389.title: Dirty Dancing: Havana Nights
305389.description: Rogue One's Diego Luna seduces the audience--and Romola Garai's character--in this sequel to the '80s classic. A young woman falls in love with a local in 1950s Cuba.

306935.title: Lars and The Real Girl
306935.description: A delusional young man strikes up an unconventional relationship with a doll he finds on the Internet in this weird and warm comedy.

312170.title: Charlie Bartlett
312170.description: A cheeky high schooler sells prescription drugs to the kids of his new school while offering pseudo-psychiatric advice from a bathroom stall.

312172.title: Copying Beethoven
312172.description: In the days before the first performance of his Ninth Symphony, Beethoven needs help with copying the manuscript, so a promising student of composition, Anna Holtz, is sent to assist him. During the next two years, the final ones of Beethoven's life, Anna provides assistance to the deaf, temperamental, ailing man. In return, he tutors her in composition and explains to her the ideas and principles of Romanticism. Pushed away by Beethoven's derision of her work, Anna ultimately returns to find him near death. As he dictates his final compositions to Anna, Beethoven finally acknowledges that she is now free to become the composer she was always meant to be.

312201.title: Wild Bill
312201.description: Wild Bill Hickok is a hard-drinking, quick-shooting gunslinger who faces the showdown of his life in this exciting, visually stunning tale.

312412.title: The Black Stallion
312412.description: A heartwarming adventure about a boy who forges a special friendship with a wild stallion after both are shipwrecked on a deserted island.

316455.title: Sorority Row
316455.description: Five sorority sisters take a prank too far, resulting in tragedy, but cover up the incident until it comes back to haunt them a year later.

316456.title: The Spy Next Door
316456.description: A man asked to baby-sit his neighbor's children winds up having to fight off secret agents after one of the kids inadvertently downloads a secret code.

321856.title: The Blair Witch Project
321856.description: A trio of filmmakers trek to uncover an urban legend, becomes an excursion into heart-stopping terror, in the original "found footage" horror.

321857.title: Book of Shadows: Blair Witch 2
321857.description: Four fans of the original BLAIR WITCH movie descend into a nightmare of murder, madness and supernatural horror in this sequel to the horror classic.

326900.title: Things Never Said
326900.description: After years of dealing with an abusive husband, a Los Angeles woman finds her passion for slam poetry and dreams of one day performing in New York.

342062.title: The Secret of the Nutcracker
342062.description: In this version of the famous Christmas story, young Clara takes a magical journey on Christmas Eve to find her father in the midst of World War II.

348456.title: The Good, the Bad and the Ugly
348456.description: Clint Eastwood portrays the invincible "Man With No Name" in a lethal pursuit of $200,000 in Confederate money.  Lee Van Cleef and Eli Wallach also star in this renowned western.

348932.title: Escape Plan
348932.description: An incarcerated structural engineer teams up with another inmate to break out of a top-secret, high-security prison in this non-stop action-thriller.

349284.title: American Ghost Hunter
349284.description: In this unbelievable documentary, a paranormal investigator makes his way to his hometown in Iowa to release his family from decades of ghostly bonds.

355682.title: Blown Away
355682.description: A mad bomber terrorizes Boston, targeting the bomb squad, forcing an eventual confrontation between the bomber and the head of the squad.

375599.title: The Magnificent Seven
375599.description: Yul Brynner stars as one of seven master gunmen pitted against an army of marauding bandits in this rousing action tale that launched the film careers of Steve McQueen, Charles Bronson and James Coburn.

375600.title: A Fistful of Dollars
375600.description: A stranger in San Miguel becomes involved in a vendetta between two families. Playing one family against the other, he rescues a beautiful woman from captivity.

380515.title: Child 44
380515.description: Set in the Soviet Union, an exiled secret police officer hunts a serial killer murdering children, but the trail leads to an internal cover-up.

389515.title: Griffin and Phoenix
389515.description: A poignant romantic comedy about two people who face a seemingly insurmountable obstacle that may stand between them and a last chance at love.

394073.title: Baby Boom
394073.description: J.C. receives news that she has inherited a baby girl from a relative. After failing to get the baby adopted by another couple, the child becomes very attached to J.C., who reluctantly keeps the youngster. Eventually the child's mischief leads to a series of comical events that cost J.C. her job and her boyfriend, but lead her to invent an applesauce recipe for children that makes her a very wealthy woman.

401466.title: Four Weddings and a Funeral
401466.description: An Englishman meets an American woman at a wedding, but his inability to express his feelings forestalls any chance at love, until they meet again...and again.

404570.title: Heartbreakers
404570.description: A mother/daughter pair of cons set up wealthy man by marrying, seducing and then bilking them but their final con together gets far more complicated.

407968.title: What to Expect When You're Expecting
407968.description: A heartfelt comedy about five couples whose intertwined lives are turned upside down by the challenges of impending parenthood.

437407.title: V/H/S
437407.description: A group of misfits burglarize a desolate house to acquire a rare tape but instead they find a dead body and endless amounts of terrifying footage.

437414.title: Tucker & Dale vs. Evil
437414.description: A group of college kids mistake Tucker and Dale for killer hillbillies and, when one goes missing, the misconception grows—along with the body count.

437415.title: Deadfall
437415.description: On the run after a casino heist, a brother and sister go their separate ways on divergent paths, making their inevitable reunion potentially deadly.

437418.title: Boarding Gate
437418.description: From Olivier Assayas comes an erotic thriller about a former prostitute and her onetime pimp-turned-high powered businessman at the center of it.

441248.title: Tortilla Soup
441248.description: A Mexican-American master chef and father to three daughters has lost his taste for food but not for life.

453672.title: A Long Way Down
453672.description: On New Year’s Eve, four strangers, intent on ending it all, fatefully meet on a London rooftop, where they create a dysfunctional family and a Plan B.

456403.title: Woman Thou Art Loosed
456403.description: A life of dysfunction and abuse entagles a woman in the world of drugs, prostitution and imprisonment, but her healing begins behind bars.

456554.title: The Jewish Cardinal
456554.description: THE JEWISH CARDINAL tells the amazing true story of Jean-Marie Lustiger, the son of Polish-Jewish immigrants, who maintained his cultural identity as a Jew even after converting to Catholicism at a young age, and later joining the priesthood. Quickly rising within the ranks of the Church, Lustiger was appointed Archbishop of Paris by Pope Jean Paul II - and found a new platform to celebrate his dual identity as a Catholic Jew, earning him both friends and enemies from either group. When Carmelite nuns settle down to build a convent within the cursed walls of Auschwitz, Lustiger finds himself a mediator between the two communities - and may be forced at last to choose his side.

457132.title: Spare Parts
457132.description: Based on a true story, four undocumented students form a robotics club defy the odds to compete against the nation's top universities.

460057.title: Marauders
460057.description: An untraceable group of elite bank robbers is chased by an FBI agent who uncovers a deeper conspiracy behind the robbery-homicides.

461204.title: The Forbidden Kingdom
461204.description: A mystical staff transports an American teen to China, where he joins a band of martial-arts warriors to free the imprisoned Monkey King.

462501.title: Two Wrongs
462501.description: A single mother confronts a parent's worst nightmare when her daughter is abducted and she must do the unthinkable to find her.

462503.title: Early Release
462503.description: After being released from jail, a suburban housewife's life is threatened again when her former cellmate unexpectedly appears and invades her world.

462511.title: Amber Alert
462511.description: A man takes a bus full of children hostage in an attempt to receive ransom money from an insurance company that denied his very sick mother's claim.

462516.title: Do No Harm
462516.description: Emily Edmunds has a great job and a great guy, Mark. But when Mark is killed in a plane crash, a distraught Emily attempts suicide.

462521.title: Brace for Impact
462521.description: A flight crash investigator is haunted by her brother's ghost after leaving him on a plane she knew was going down, leading her to seek redemption.

462523.title: Run to Me
462523.description: Alison Wynn is an amateur triathlete who convinces Dr. Laura Stevens, a controversial peak-performance trainer, to take her on as a client. Together they embark on a rigorous program combining cutting-edge physical training with experimental hypnotherapy in an effort to render Alison more competitive. Pushed to her limits and forced to explore the painful repressed memories of her mother's suicide, Dr. Stevens' punishing regimen helps Alison post impressive gains and break through her own glass ceiling; but at what cost?

462749.title: Look Again
462749.description: After a young woman's boyfriend is murdered by an intruder, things worsen when she meets her friend's new boyfriend and suspects him to be the killer.

462751.title: Serialized
462751.description: After getting dropped by her publisher, celebrated novelist Hannah Ryan uses the negative forces in her life to inspire the creation of a pulp crime serial that posts new chapters to subscriber's devices every week. The initial release is a modest success but the work becomes a massive hit after a real life murder takes place that bears a striking similarity to Hannah's story. Is it really just a coincidence or is it possible that a copycat serial killer is acting out the fictitious murders in real life? And is he going to strike again once Hannah releases her next chapter?

462761.title: First Response
462761.description: A gunman forces a paramedic to drive an ambulance, while his partner treats the man's injured brother.

462763.title: Sometimes the Good Kill
462763.description: After a mysterious death at the Abbey, Sister Talia finds herself caught in the center of the internal investigation. With strict orders from the newly elected Mother Superior, she must uncover the truth behind the death and ensure the Abbey remains undisturbed. Things take a sharp turn when another sister is found murdered and Sister Talia is forced to find the killer.

462771.title: Trigger Point
462771.description: Callie finds herself affected by big business politics and decides to join an activist group to do something about it.

462773.title: Crossfire
462773.description: When a soldier returns from Iraq, she must deal with PTSD, making a normal life as well as becoming the target of an obsessed soldier seeking revenge.

462800.title: Enron: the Smartest Guys in the Room
462800.description: The rise and fall of Enron is the focus as executives got rich pretending the company was more profitable while lower-level employees lost everything.

462874.title: Swept Under
462874.description: When a crime scene cleaner discovers evidence has been left behind, she rushes to search for a killer's identity with the help of a newbie detective.

463124.title: Burden of Evil
463124.description: When a psychopath kidnaps a powerful senator’s daughter, he requests a lead detective whose husband was just killed by the same sadistic criminal.

465208.title: Cottage Country
465208.description: A man’s planned marriage proposal to his lady at a lake cabin goes awry when a fight with his brother leads to murder and more killings to hide it.

468475.title: My Heroes Have Always Been Cowboys
468475.description: A rowdy rodeo rider gets injured bull-riding and plans to hang up his spurs, but a visit with his ailing dad forces him to be a hero one more time.

469312.title: Getting High
469312.description: A New York City artist battling drug addiction completes a spiritual journey with his best friend that goes back to the Underground Railroad.

469619.title: Cheech and Chong's Next Movie
469619.description: The zany, stoner twosome return for more misadventures as Cheech loses his job, deals with an angry neighbor and tries to appeal to a sexy lady.

469688.title: For Richer Or Poorer
469688.description: A couple who are in serious trouble with the IRS get the culture shock of their lives when they pretend to be an Amish couple in Pennsylvania.

469694.title: The Babe
469694.description: Drinking hard and playing harder, Babe Ruth rose above his hideous childhood to dominate baseball and rescue it from the brink of extinction.

471290.title: Crystal
471290.description: A promise to her dead mother is all that 10 year old Crystal has left. Will she break it to save herself, or keep it and be sold again? Nandar Pictures presents CRYSTAL, based on a true story and starring Trinity Rose Miller and Jason London.

472114.title: Free Angela and All Political Prisoners
472114.description: The story of professor Angela Davis, whose social activism implicated her in a botched kidnapping and put her on the FBI’s Most Wanted List in 1970.

472209.title: Airbnb Nightmares
472209.description: Unbelievable true stories about nightmare tenants whose actions in other people’s beloved homes go beyond dirty rooms and ransacked properties.

472215.title: The Real Antony and Cleopatra
472215.description: Filmed in historic locations, expert interviews and fascinating storytelling make up this dramatic life story of the Egyptian Queen Cleopatra.

474406.title: Psycho Sideshow: Demon Freaks
474406.description: Horror film studio Full Moon returns with shocking moments from their catalog of films, hosted from an animated, terrifying amusement park from hell.

474417.title: Evil Bong 2: Devil's Harvest
474417.description: The bizarre side-effects of a weed session with Evil Bong leads a group of pals to South America for a cure, but deadly powerful King Bong is waiting.

474418.title: Evil Bong 3: Reefer Madness
474418.description: A galactic stoner comedy about survivors of a battle with King Bong whose Venice Beach head shop gets them enslaved by an alien’s sexy weed strain.

476205.title: Nerdland
476205.description: A struggling actor and screenwriter try to make up for what they lack in brains and talent on an attention-grabbing spree to become famous in one day.

476667.title: Still Mine
476667.description: The heartfelt tale of an elderly man who comes up against the system when he sets out to build a more suitable house for his sick wife.

476670.title: Nobel Son
476670.description: The night before an arrogant chemist receives the Nobel Prize, his son is kidnapped, but he refuses to pay the ransom, and a venomous tale unfolds.

478157.title: Invisible: The Chronicles of Benjamin Knight
478157.description: After a lab accident, an American scientist gains the superpower of invisibility. Can he take control of his newfound ability to save the day?

479885.title: Angela
479885.description: A woman helps her husband run his shop, and the shady business behind it. She tires of their life of crime, but finds herself falling deeper into it.

479916.title: Sacrifice
479916.description: An undercover cop inadvertently gets involved in a heroin ring when a young defector of the drug trade leaves his five year-old sister in his care.

480226.title: Gacy
480226.description: He appeared to be a model citizen, father, and husband. This film dives into the psyche of this serial killer, who murdered over thirty men and boys.

485731.title: This Beautiful Fantastic
485731.description: A young woman who dreams of being a children's author makes an unlikely friendship with a cantankerous, rich old widower.

485984.title: Vice
485984.description: Welcome to the the ultimate resort where customers can play out their most violent fantasies with artificial inhabitants who look like humans, until one escapes.

486568.title: Music from Another Room
486568.description: A man's search for his one true love, whose birth he assisted in as a five-year-old.

487952.title: Illuminata
487952.description: When a turn-of-the-20th-century theater troupe rejects their playwright’s new opus, a melodrama builds around an influential critic and a seductress.

490104.title: Harpies
490104.description: A museum security guard gets caught in a supernatural adventure when thieves attempt to steal an ancient artifact with mysterious powers.

494929.title: Black Road
494929.description: In the lawless world of 2029, a military drifter risks his life to protect a woman from her dangerous ex, with the help of his AI friend and partner.

499511.title: Man on Wire
499511.description: Philippe Petit, who walked an illegally rigged highwire between NYC’s twin towers in 1974, faces stupendous challenges for the sake of his daring art.

499789.title: Bad Behavior
499789.description: A twist on “the call is coming from inside the house,” an unsuspecting babysitter is trapped overnight and under attack by those she least suspects.

504100.title: Point Blank
504100.description: A man is torn between gangsters and the police when his pregnant wife is abducted and a mobster forces him into crime in order to see his wife again.

504102.title: Limelight
504102.description: The king of the New York City club scene for years sees his empire crumble when DEA agents, ecstasy investigations, murder, and club culture collide.

506693.title: Titanic: The Aftermath
506693.description: This historical doc explores the aftermath of the Titanic's tragic sinking in April 1912. How were future sea travel regulations revised?

506703.title: How the Devil Got His Horns
506703.description: Art historian Alastair Sooke investigates the history of imagery surrounding Satan, and how medieval art changed the perception of the dark figure.

507637.title: The Answer Man
507637.description: A reclusive author whose book on God is a massive bestseller finds his life upended until he meets a single mother with her own ways of salvation.

507692.title: The Queen of Spain
507692.description: Affectionate comedy-drama about the world’s biggest movie star who returns to Spain, under the dictatorship of Franco Nero, to play Queen Isabella.

508260.title: Longing Nights
508260.description: Four twenty-somethings, two men and two women, navigate the nightlife of Madrid, Spain as a way to bridge the erotic loneliness in their lives.

511187.title: The Architect
511187.description: A struggle with potential consequences for all erupts after an activist exposes the dangers of the building an architect designed that she lives in.

511575.title: A Thousand Years of Good Prayers
511575.description: A woman moves from China to America to start over, When her father visits, they clash, exposing lies and family secrets from the Cultural Revolution.

518182.title: Saturday Church
518182.description: A 14-year-old boy navigating his gender identity and religious convictions turns to a fantasy world to escape his everyday inner city oppressions.

522410.title: Submergence
522410.description: A Scotsman held captive by Jihadist fighters remembers a night he spent with a woman last Christmas, who also recalls their passionate romance.

526431.title: Down by Love
526431.description: Inspired by true events in 2011, the married warden of a Versailles prison and a female inmate set off a national firestorm when they fall in love.

526688.title: In Harmony
526688.description: A brief encounter changes the lives of two very different people: an insurance company caseworker and an equestrian stuntman with a traumatic injury.

536526.title: Black Cop
536526.description: A Black, off-duty policeman is pushed to the edge by a traumatic profiling incident and takes revenge on the privileged community he swore to protect.

546980.title: Clive Barker's Lord of Illusions
546980.description: While on assignment in LA, a New York private eye stumbles into a case full of supernatural intrigue when a cult leader and illusionist is murdered.

550612.title: The Student and Mr Henri
550612.description: A grumpy old man offers a free room in his apartment to an attractive student in exchange for her promise to help break up his son’s marriage.

553874.title: Bleeding Steel
553874.description: While tracking down a deranged super-villainess, a Hong Kong detective discovers a biochemical device has been implanted into his missing daughter.

554264.title: Scream 4
554264.description: Wes Craven’s final film sees the original survivors of the Ghostface murders return to face a deadly spree again in a new decade with new surprises.

554502.title: Brooklyn's Finest
554502.description: Throughout one week, the lives of three very different New York City police officers change as a result of a violent drug operation.

555383.title: The Heart of Man
555383.description: An honest telling of the personal costs of breaking promises and following lust, as well as God’s redemptive journey back into hope.

555847.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married?
555847.description: Based on Perry's popular stage play, this is the story of a group of friends on a retreat who are about to get real about the trials of married life.

555899.title: Phat Beach
555899.description: Fun-loving teen Durrel convinces his burger-flipping pal Benny to ditch the apron for a summer of gawking at girls in Southern California.

557051.title: Eye of the Beholder
557051.description: A reclusive and tormented surveillance pro on assignment becomes fascinated with a mysterious con artist who might be a serial killer with no limits.

569299.title: Sir Noface
569299.description: A chronicle of the Australian government-sanctioned paranormal investigation on a World War II naval base that produced some unexplained results.

570252.title: Kin
570252.description: After using a mysterious weapon to protect his family, a young man goes on the run with his older brother, hoping to evade otherworldly soldiers.

579298.title: Tyler Perry's Madea's Witness Protection
579298.description: The law’s takedown of a Wall Street banker who ran a Ponzi scheme is nothing compared to having to live with his family in hiding at Madea’s house!

582027.title: Killing Them Softly
582027.description: When a duo of inept crooks are hired to rob a mob-run poker game and crush the local criminal economy, vengeance is sought via a reluctant hitman.

585058.title: Paper Soldiers
585058.description: An overeager thief joins a crew of equally inefficient burglars, in this outrageous comedy which depicts the rocky life of a criminal.

585148.title: Mallrats
585148.description: Male best friends, dumped by their girlfriends, spend the day strategizing at a local mall, in this funny, crude, and screamingly offensive offering.

586151.title: The Andromeda Strain (1971)
586151.description: Follow Michael Crichton’s intense story of a scientific team working around the clock to stop an alien germ brought back by a space probe.

594961.title: Cyborg
594961.description: A cyborg on a quest to cure the world of a plague with a vaccine is captured by cannibals who plot to steal the antidote and rule the world.

595266.title: Blood Hunters: Rise of the Hybrids
595266.description: An avenging aswang killer teams up with a hybrid and a team of demon hunters to attack the lair of the most powerful underworld warlords.

595272.title: Camp Twilight
595272.description: A weekend getaway turns into a living nightmare when a mysterious killer terrorizes six students at a campground.

595274.title: Sweet Tastes of Souls
595274.description: When four struggling band members stop at a lonely roadside cafe for a slice of pie they find themselves imprisoned in the deranged cafe owners bizarre art collection and must battle a sinister force with an appetite for souls.

595276.title: White Lie
595276.description: A university student who fakes a cancer diagnosis for the attention and financial gain struggles to maintain her secret.

595841.title: I Used to Be Normal: A Boyband Fangirl Story
595841.description: Four diverse women had their lives dramatically changed by their love of a boy band - Backstreet Boys, One Direction, Take That and The Beatles.

600044.title: Reprisal
600044.description: After surviving a brutal armed robbery, a Cincinnati father teams up with his ex-cop neighbor to track down the ruthless killer and avenge the assault.

601430.title: Femalien: Cosmic Crush
601430.description: While participating in an archaeological expedition on a distant moon, students are turned into the willing sex slaves of its insatiable ruler.

602506.title: Slither
602506.description: When an alien organism attacks a small town, a devoted wife must accept that her husband has transformed from the man she married.

604500.title: Wargames
604500.description: Would you like to play a game? Computer hacker David Lightman (Matthew Broderick) can break the most intricate secret codes and master even the most difficult computer games. But when he unwittingly taps into the Defense Department's war computer, he initiates a confrontation of global proportions -- World War III. Together with his girlfriend (Ally Sheedy) and a computer genius (John Wood), David must race against time to outwit his opponent...and prevent a nuclear Armageddon!

610032.title: The Tall T
610032.description: After an outlaw and his gang kidnap an heiress, her nervous husband, and a rancher, the victims must outsmart their cruel captors.

610520.title: Late Spring
610520.description: Japanese cinema classic about a 27-year-old who resists calls for her to get married so that she can stay at home caring for her widowed father.

610521.title: Drunken Angel
610521.description: Akira Kurosawa’s classic about a drunken doctor in a town tested by an epidemic and the yakuza mafia who clashes and bonds with a wounded gangster.

615648.title: The Groomsmen
615648.description: A groom (Ed Burns) and his four attendants wrestle with issues related to friendship and maturity a week before the big day.

615899.title: I Could Never Be Your Woman
615899.description: A mother falls for a younger man while her daughter falls in love for the first time. Mother Nature messes with their fates.

619916.title: Call Me King
619916.description: In the international world of gun running, where only one can rule, loyalty, honor, and discretion are tested, as is the priceless bond of family.

620759.title: Lone Star Deception
620759.description: While running for Governor of Texas, a man has an affair with a prostitute, which threatens to derail his political ambitions for good.

622280.title: Sister Code
622280.description: In the absence of their recently passed mother, three foster sisters with very different personalities struggle to navigate love, life, and family.

625413.title: The Scorpion King: Book of Souls
625413.description: When an evil warlord gains a sword that can steal souls, the Scorpion King and the sister of a Nubian king must find the one thing that can stop him.

625415.title: The Scorpion King 4: Quest for Power
625415.description: After the legendary Scorpion King is betrayed by a friend, he takes on an entire kingdom to prevent an evil leader from seizing an unstoppable power.

625417.title: The Scorpion King 2: Rise of a Warrior
625417.description: After an evil general murders his father, the Scorpion King descends into the underworld to face a fearsome foe and reclaim the Sword of Damocles.

625420.title: The Scorpion King 3: Battle for Redemption
625420.description: When the Scorpion King is hired to guard a beleaguered king, things are not as they seem, so it is up to him and a lady assassin to save Scandinavia.

626763.title: Above Suspicion
626763.description: “Game of Thrones” star Emilia Clarke leads this true crime thriller as an informant whose help with an FBI agent leads to a deadly aftermath.

626771.title: An Ordinary Man
626771.description: Academy Award-winner Ben Kingsley headlines this dramatic thriller as a fugitive war criminal caught in a game of wits and peril with his housekeeper.

629233.title: Empire
629233.description: The gritty South Bronx meets the white-collar world of Wall Street, when a drug dealer betrays his pals and neighborhood to make a shady investment.

629330.title: Eliminators
629330.description: After a former U.S. federal agent’s home is invaded and his daughter is put in danger, he must leave the witness protection program to save her life.

630920.title: Drop Dead Fred
630920.description: Desperate for escape from her cheating husband and a life of ennui, a young woman gets an overdue visit from her impish imaginary childhood friend.

637552.title: Out of the Furnace
637552.description: When his ex-Marine little brother disappears after joining a notorious crime syndicate, a Rust Belt steel worker gets armed and goes after him.

639186.title: Cheech and Chong Get Out of My Room
639186.description: Cheech and Chong ramp up the laughs as the comedy stoner legends headline a Los Angeles-based mockumentary about their daily lives.

640068.title: Mike Wallace is Here
640068.description: Journalist Mike Wallace’s iconic and legendary news career and the subjects he so deftly interviewed is shown here over decades of world events.

640112.title: Tyrel
640112.description: A friends’ weekend retreat takes a disastrous turn for the only member of the group who is Black, who begins to feel like he’s being targeted.

640197.title: Cold Case Hammarskjöld
640197.description: A director and private investigator put the pieces together surrounding the mysterious death of Swedish economist and diplomat Dag Hammarskjöld.

643079.title: For a Few Dollars More
643079.description: In this classic, truly great spaghetti western, a keen, quick-witted bounty hunter and his fierce rival follow the bloody trail of a murderous outlaw.

647082.title: Doomsday
647082.description: Nearly 30 years after a deadly epidemic swept through Scotland, a commander and her crew search for an antidote when the virus emerges in London.

651741.title: Xingu
651741.description: Three brothers set out on a mission throughout Brazil, and in the process befriend many indigenous tribes, sparking an idea to create a national park.

654055.title: The Jerk
654055.description: Steve Martin makes his film-starring debut in the wacky comedy hit The Jerk. From rags to riches... to rags, the laughter never stops!

655333.title: Babysitter's Black Book
655333.description: When family money problems threaten a whiz kid’s dreams for college, she and her friends turn their babysitting gigs into an escort service for dads.

657037.title: Land of the Lost
657037.description: Comedy genius Will Ferrell stars as a has-been scientist, who gets more than he bargained for, when his expedition takes a wrong turn into hilarity.

657079.title: Let's Go to Prison
657079.description: When Fate steers a career criminal’s plot for revenge off-course, he sends his intended victim’s kid to prison, and then joins him in the slammer.

659802.title: A Common Man
659802.description: A mysterious man plants five massive bombs in the city of Colombo, Sri Lanka, threatening to detonate them unless terrorists are released from prison.

664874.title: Carrie
664874.description: An adaptation of the classic novel. Carrie, a girl with telekinetic powers, teaches her classmates a deadly lesson when they humiliate her at prom.

667306.title: Unsheltered
667306.description: After seeking shelter from a vicious storm, five college students are reported missing. They escaped mother nature, but can they escape their deaths?

671595.title: ECCO
671595.description: A former assassin, now living a new life in the shadows with his family, emerges from hiding to discover the origin of his lethal beginnings.

672234.title: Meet the Blacks
672234.description: After Carl Black moves his family to Beverly Hills, their arrival is timed with the city's annual purge, where all crime is legal for 12 hours.

680184.title: Crypto (Sub Esp)
680184.description: Demoted back to his hometown in upstate New York, a Wall Street banker puts his family in danger when he investigates a tangled web of corruption.

681622.title: Parkland
681622.description: A recounting of the chaotic events that occurred at Dallas' Parkland Hospital on the day U.S. President John F. Kennedy was assassinated.

682615.title: The Bourne Ultimatum
682615.description: Jason Bourne flees a new generation of skilled CIA operatives in a non-stop race around the globe while seeking the truth behind his mysterious past.

682626.title: Get Him to the Greek
682626.description: Aspiring music exec Aaron Green has just 72 hours to deliver rock legend Aldous Snow to LA, navigating a minefield of mayhem to get there.

682628.title: The Bourne Legacy
682628.description: Agent Aaron Cross uses his genetically enhanced skills to evade the CIA after Jason Bourne's actions lead to the termination of his black ops program.

691877.title: The Raven
691877.description: A young Baltimore detective joins forces with Edgar Allan Poe to stop a madman from  committing horrific murders inspired by the writer’s own works.

692267.title: The Mighty Quinn
692267.description: The murder of a prominent businessman on a tiny Caribbean island plunges a police chief into the decadent lives of the island's white establishment.

694227.title: The Rundown
694227.description: A wild action-adventure about a bounty hunter named Beck, who's searching for a rebellious mobster's son and a priceless treasure in the Amazon.

695331.title: Missing Link
695331.description: Mr. Link recruits explorer Sir Lionel Frost and adventurer Adelina Fortnight to help find his long-lost relatives in the fabled valley of Shangri-La.

698158.title: Neon
698158.description: A celebration of the beauty, invention, design and heritage of one of the trademark symbols of 20th century technology and electronics: the neon sign.

701770.title: Danger Close
701770.description: Major Harry Smith leads 108 novice soldiers into an impossible battle in Vietnam that challenges their courage to triumph against overwhelming odds.

706386.title: C.O.G.
706386.description: Based on a David Sedaris short story, a closeted Yale dropout goes off the grid to pick apples at a rural Oregon orchard among religious zealots.

707020.title: Witches in the Woods
707020.description: A group gets stranded during an off-the-grid snowboarding trip. As the temperature falls, tensions ratchet up, turning into a literal witch hunt.

707923.title: DC 9/11: Time of Crisis
707923.description: This docudrama film looks inside the Bush Administration, beginning with the terrorist attacks on Sept. 11, 2001, and the weeks after.

711013.title: Mid90s
711013.description: A 13-year-old spends his summer navigating a troubled home life and skating with a crew of new friends.

711406.title: Take Me Home Tonight
711406.description: Four years after graduation, an awkward genius uses his sister's boyfriend's party as the perfect occasion to make his move on his high school crush.

713500.title: Where'd You Go, Bernadette
713500.description: After sacrificing her creative ambitions to raise her kids and support her husband, a middle-aged woman embarks on a journey to rediscover herself.

714936.title: Hex
714936.description: Following a mysterious disappearance on a jump, a group of skydivers experiences paranormal occurrences that leave them fighting for their lives.

715626.title: The Lifeguard
715626.description: Tired of an unfulfilling career, a 29-year-old returns to her childhood home in Connecticut, gets a job as a lifeguard, and starts dating a teenager.

724345.title: Identity Thief
724345.description: A hilarious blockbuster hit about an accounts representative who has one week to clear his name after a con artist steals his identity.

724349.title: The Scorpion King
724349.description: The spectacular Mummy series explodes into a new realm of non-stop action following the epic story of the most feared warrior of the ancient world.

724351.title: Death Becomes Her
724351.description: When a jealous actress discovers an immortality treatment, she decides to take advantage of it to become young again and outshine her rival.

100000038.title: Dirty Dancing: Television Special
100000038.description: A TV remake of the 1987 classic about a teen who gets swept up in a secret tryst with a dancer employed by the resort where her family is summering.

100000057.title: Somebody's Child
100000057.description: A chance meeting between an ex-con and the twin brother he never knew he had brings long overdue reconciliation and redemption to one special family.

100000192.title: The Wicked
100000192.description: On a dangerous dare, a group of teenagers investigate the local lore of a flesh-eating immortal witch living deep in the woods and discover its truth.

100000384.title: The Love Punch
100000384.description: After a corrupt businessman destroys their retirement savings, a divorced couple travels to France to steal his fiancée’s multimillion-dollar diamond.

100000580.title: Ali G Indahouse
100000580.description: Ali G, a white gangsta-rapper wannabe, gets hilariously entangled in an evil Chancellor’s plot to overthrow Great Britain’s Prime Minister.

100000720.title: I Now Pronounce You Chuck & Larry
100000720.description: In order to receive domestic partner benefits, two straight Brooklyn firefighters are forced to improvise as love-struck newlyweds.

100000721.title: MacGruber
100000721.description: The former special forces operative and his sidekick set out on a mission to recover a stolen nuclear warhead from his sworn enemy, VonCunth.

100000722.title: Beautiful Creatures
100000722.description: Two women try to outwit the law and pull off a fake ransom scam after one of them accidentally kills the other's abusive boyfriend.

100000723.title: Altered
100000723.description: From the writer-director of The Blair Witch Project comes this story of four men who are out to get the alien life form that killed their friends.

100000724.title: Bruce Almighty
100000724.description: An encounter with God leaves a frustrated, wannabe news anchor for a Buffalo TV network with divine power and a life-altering challenge.

100000849.title: All Eyez on Me
100000849.description: This biopic chronicles the ascent of hip-hop legend and activist Tupac Shakur centering on the relationships and experiences that shaped his artistry.

100000850.title: Booksmart
100000850.description: About to graduate, two best friends try to cram four years of fun into one night after spending their high school years entirely focused on studying.

100000867.title: Howard the Duck
100000867.description: A fast-talking, cigar-chomping, beer-loving duck is transported to Earth from a parallel universe and must save the planet from an alien invasion.

100000868.title: Harry and the Hendersons
100000868.description: On the way home from a camping trip in the mountains, the Henderson family encounters a friendly Sasquatch and helps him evade a malicious hunter.

100000869.title: Far and Away
100000869.description: Two young Irish immigrants flee their home country on a ship bound for America, where they find love and new possibilities in its dangerous frontiers.

100001703.title: Tyler Perry's Acrimony
100001703.description: A faithful wife tired of standing by her devious husband is enraged when it becomes clear she has been betrayed by him financially.

100001741.title: Nerve
100001741.description: A high school senior finds herself immersed in an online game of truth or dare, where her every move becomes manipulated by a community of "watchers."

100002618.title: Back to 1942
100002618.description: A deadly drought in 1942 takes its toll on central China's Henan province during the war against Japan.
